It is the simple client-server application based on Java 7.

Clone application by 'git clone git@github.com:kd41/wallet.git' command.

Database is build on hsql.

Run server by 'ant all' command.

Run client by 'ant -DuserName=[userName] run' command, where [userName] is a String. For example 'ant -DuserName=alex run'.

The application configuration can be changed in 'wallet.properties' file.

Logs located in '/logs' folder.